1. *Cigarete* su mi najveća slabost. (Cigarettes are my biggest weakness.)
2. U prodavnici sam kupio kutiju *cigareta*. (I bought a pack of cigarettes at the store.)
3. Nažalost, moj prijatelj puši previše *cigareta*. (Unfortunately, my friend smokes too many cigarettes.)
4. Nisam mogao da se fokusiram na posao jer sam bio bez *cigareta*. (I couldn't focus on work because I was out of cigarettes.)
5. Mnogi ljudi se trude da prestanu da puše *cigarete*. (Many people are trying to quit smoking cigarettes.)
6. *Cigarete* su štetne po zdravlje. (Cigarettes are harmful to health.)
7. Jako je teško ostaviti *cigarete*. (It's very difficult to quit smoking cigarettes.)
8. Država je povećala porez na *cigarete* radi smanjenja potrošnje. (The government has increased taxes on cigarettes to reduce consumption.)
9. Moja majka je bila ljuta kad je pronašla moje *cigarete*. (My mother was angry when she found my cigarettes.)
10. Nikad ne pušim više od jedne *cigarete* dnevno. (I never smoke more than one cigarette a day.)